<p>主料</p> 
<p>猪肉馅(150g)，海虾(5只)，馄饨皮(适量)，香油(少许)，紫菜(少许)，虾皮(少许)</p> 
<p>辅料</p> 
<p>葱(10g)，姜(3g)，美极鲜(10ml)，酱油(5ml)，花生油(25ml)，五香粉(2g)</p> 
<p>厨具</p> 
<p>煮锅</p> 
<p>步骤</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//a115/a115de1b077db7fd87e0930df9e694cc.com/large/16c30006d7f2a0550750"></p> 
<p>1、猪肉馅加入所有的调料拌匀。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//27c4/27c44d816b82e2b4e847fbb2af31fedc.com/large/16c200035aac43de7f11"></p> 
<p>2、海虾去壳取出虾仁。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5480/5480cc2b9ef6abd5608394be402b2f2a.com/large/16c40006edc86d1b9a93"></p> 
<p>3、剁成虾茸。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//ca87/ca87a002ff06c151cb48341b9470854e.com/large/16c9000845dc697c686f"></p> 
<p>4、放入肉馅中拌匀。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6eaf/6eaf2864d06e04da647e5f1bb0d72035.com/large/16c8000018c66fbd23a5"></p> 
<p>5、和好的肉馅加馄饨皮包成小馄饨。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//85dc/85dce504c181808274213b4cec7a452d.com/large/16c9000845dd54e3e730"></p> 
<p>6、黄瓜去皮洗净切片。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//dd43/dd432d0b0f253ad4ee7ededafa9988d2.com/large/16c8000018c51bc7d8f6"></p> 
<p>7、再碗中加入适量的紫菜和虾皮。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8e56/8e56118977ebdba094f06f11f437392a.com/large/16c30006d7f33070dec5"></p> 
<p>8、馄饨和黄瓜一起煮熟。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//09aa/09aaeabe71a741434b7fa34088f94de4.com/large/16c200035aade085014f"></p> 
<p>9、加入碗中即可。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//e447/e447eec47759843c89f875919b078b87.com/large/16c200035b02c23b2030"></p> 
<p>10、成品图</p>小吃 馄饨 黄瓜 香油老妈自创馄饨新做法，一锅不够吃，学会了可以去做生意了！